title: Black Adam - It's An OK Movie
description:
So Black Adam turned out to be surprisingly... OK. Who knew? In a world of awful MCU entries and a DCEU that's struggling to find a path forward, could Black Adam finally be the breakthrough they need? 

Want to help fund the Critical Drinker's first short film? Then check out the Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1000347150/rogue-elements-a-ryan-drake-short-film
